[[!comment format=mdwn
 username="joey"
 subject="""comment 3"""
 date="2026-03-11T14:48:31Z"
 content="""
	$ git annex migrate --remove-size
	migrate data.bin
	git-annex: failed creating link from old to new key

That happens when the file is not present in the local repository.
If you get the file first it will work.

Migrate needs the content present so it can populate the new key.
Otherwise, there can be situation where the new key never ends up being
populated with the content.
"""]]
